---
import Header from "../components/header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/footer.astro";
import "../styling/main.css";
import "../styling/booking.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Assistant&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <title>About</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header><Header /></header>
    <main>
      <h1>Booking</h1>
      <section>
      <img class="bookingwave" src="/images/bookingwave.svg" alt="" />
      <p>Skriv dine ønsker og kontaktinformation i formularen herunder, så vender jeg tilbage til dig hurtigst muligt, så vi kan lave en aftale sammen. Hvis du foretrækker at kontakte mig på anden vis, så kig nederst på hjemmesiden. Der finder du mit telefonnummer og links til mine sociale medier.</p>
      <div class="booking_form">
        <form>
          <label for="fname">Fornavn</label><br />
          <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" /><br />
          <label for="lname">Efternavn</label><br />
          <input type="text" id="lname" name="lname" /><br />
          <label for="email">Email</label><br />
          <input type="text" id="email" name="email" /><br />
          <label for="phone">Telefonnummer</label><br />
          <input type="text" id="phone" name="phone" /><br />
          <label for="subject">Subject</label><br />
          <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" /><br />
          <label for="text">Message</label><br />
          <input type="text" id="message" name="message" /><br />
          <div class="submit_container">
            <input type="submit" value="Submit" id="submit" />
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer><Footer /></footer>
  </body>
</html>
